                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/8645: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-05-27T22:00:00+09:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 27, 1921—10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received May 28—4:52 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>189. following from Vladivostok: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“May 27, 5 p.m. Night quiet, fighting resumed 8 o’clock in the morning
                            lasted thirty minutes. By noon the Japanese disarmed police barracks
                            where the late ministers gathered. Total casualties perhaps twenty.
                            Situation insecure.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
